This paper discusses the performance of deep neural networks for function approximation, which is a common topic in machine learning and artificial intelligence. Therefore, the most likely sub-category is cs.LG (Machine Learning), followed by cs.NE (Neural and Evolutionary Computing) and cs.AI (Artificial Intelligence). The paper also mentions the use of neural networks for image processing (cs.CV) and signal processing (cs.SI), which are also possible sub-categories.
